{"title_page": "Arindam Sharma", "text_new": "{{EngvarB|date = April 2020}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Arindam Sharma\n| image              = \n| caption            = \n| birth_name         = Arindam\n| birth_date         = {{Birth date and age|df=y|1995|08|09}}\n| birth_place        = [[Jorhat]], [[Assam]], [[India]]\n| occupation         = [[Film director|Director]]\n| yearsactive        = \n| spouse             = \n}}\n\n'''Arindam Sharma''' (born 9 August) is an Indian director and screenwriter<ref>1.''{{Cite web|url=https://assamtimespost.com/?p=17846|title=\u0986\u09b9\u09bf \u0986\u099b\u09c7 \u0985\u09b8\u09ae\u09c0\u09af\u09bc\u09be\u09a4 \u098f\u0996\u09a8 \"\u099a\u09c1\u09aa\u09be\u09f0\u09b9\u09bf\u09f0\u09cb\u2019 \u099a\u09bf\u09a8\u09c7\u09ae\u09be\"\u0964 \u09a8\u09f1\u09be\u0997\u09a4 \u09aa\u09f0\u09bf\u099a\u09be\u09b2\u0995 \u0985\u09f0\u09bf\u09a8\u09cd\u09a6\u09ae \u09b6\u09f0\u09cd\u09ae\u09be\u09f0 \u09aa\u09f0\u09bf\u099a\u09be\u09b2\u09a8\u09be\u09f0\u09c7 \u09a8\u09bf\u09f0\u09cd\u09ae\u09bf\u09a4 \u098f\u0987 \u099b\u09ac\u09bf\u0996\u09a8\u09f0 \u09a8\u09be\u09ae \u09b9\u09c8\u099b\u09c7 \"AVR: Advik Vs Ray\"|last=|first=|date=|website=ASSAM TIMES POST|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}''</ref>. He made his directorial debut with the [[Assamese language|Assamese]]-language film ''[[AVR (2020 film)|AVR(2020film)]]''. released on 23 October 2020.\n\n== Filmography ==\n=== As director ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Film\n! Director\n! Writer/Dialogues\n! Screenplay\n! Story\n|-\n| 2020\n|[[AVR (2020 film)|AVR]]\n|{{yes}}\n|{{yes}}\n|{{yes}}\n|{{yes}}\n|-\n|-\n|}\n==Reference==\n", "text_old": "{{db-repost|xfd=Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Arindam Sharma|help=off}}\n\n{{EngvarB|date = April 2020}}\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date = March 2020}}\n\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Arindam Sharma\n| image              = \n| caption            